a href=\"https://read.muzikair.com/tw/news/YAMAHA的全能科技樹！不只鋼琴樂器與機車%20還有廚房與高爾夫-20521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread.muzikair.com%2Ftw%2Fnews%2FYAMAHA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E8%83%BD%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A8%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E9%8B%BC%E7%90%B4%E6%A8%82%E5%99%A8%E8%88%87%E6%A9%9F%E8%BB%8A%2520%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E8%88%87%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE%E5%A4%AB-20521.html&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=50872f4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://read.muzikair.com/tw/news/YAMAHA的全能科技樹！不只鋼琴樂器與機車%20還有廚房與高爾夫-20521.html</a>"},{"pid":"b67ae9644c08a5894860498dda1119f7d71b8df6","tid":247711,"uid":50865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T19:40:11.000Z","msg":"叫我?"}]}